CITATION: 1984 AIR 626 1981 SCR (3) 22 1981 SCC (2) 714 1981 SCALE (1)503 
ACT:
 City of Nagpur Corporation Act, 1948-Section 59(3) (b)- Municipal Commissioner is the competent authority to suspend municipal officers and servants, pending a departmental inquiry-Words and phrases "control" and "vests", explained- Criminal cases to be disposed off to protect the accused from harassment-Departmental inquiry, whether can be continued after acquittal in a criminal case.
 
